Paula is a red panda, longing to climb as many trees as possible. 
You need to help take care of Paula so she can spend more time climbing trees. 
If the green light is on, Paula is happy and content in life, and her tail will wag. 
However, after ____{enter time speriod} Paula's red light will start to flash which makes the red light flash. 
If this happens, press the heart to give Paula her medicine and the yellow light will flash. When the medicine works, keep feeding Paula and the green light will eventually come on.
